    ["T"] = "Target: Hive\'Regal Spitfires",
  },
  [8776] = {
    ["D"] = "As the war effort mounts, the silithid presence in the area presents an ever increasing threat to our operations.  You\'ve been selected to partake on an assault on Hive\'Regal where your primary target will consist of the Hive\'Regal slavemakers.$B$BReport back to Commander Mar\'alith after your task is completed.",
